\n打擊香港國際金融中心型像<br />\n機埸行街 中環行街罷工！尖沙咀行街</span>"},{"pid":"e3dc97455948fd489e8270b394c4fac056478ae8","tid":1379961,"uid":64935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:23:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cae5e646b77f6331d34997237d71181e86fdd659","tid":1379961,"uid":22254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:24:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"404911d631d349f82ed23dfc822d56e74c80ea42","tid":1379961,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:24:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c19c3c9ccea28a27df47fba4af08696da1cad003","tid":1379961,"uid":224859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483906dc3f6dc8e1eeb6f8eb4ae5ba8e2af01eca","tid":1379961,"uid":33565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:26:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d48e08b3399008af4b3871d2ec7bb0413d8f2ed","tid":1379961,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d5f5cd314fcceb56dcd8638b8ddbcc7e0ebe1d","tid":1379961,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c207533e1bbce5e0fe8616855c523671d3305da","tid":1379961,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:47:37.000Z","msg":"成日講警犬武力封頂，其實我哋都已經封左頂。<br />\n<br />\n雖然民意仲企係抗爭者一邊，但係我哋仲未逼到政府有任何根本性改變。<br />\n<br />\n因為到依家，我哋主要嘅抗爭手段未有根本性轉變。<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個禮拜，每一次行動，都係和理非遊行，到咁上下，勇武派同警犬開戰。<br />\n<br />\n每一次，柒婆只係需要出警犬同蓄龍已經頂得住，然後自己龜縮。<br />\n<br />\n每一次行動都拉3-40個勇武派，勇武派唔係無限人手架，拉一個就少一個架啦。<br />\n<br />\n如果依家嘅抗爭手段唔改變，當柒婆拉鳩晒啲勇武派之後，就正翻和理非上街，之後成個社運倒退翻去2014年之前。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋要做啲咩？我哋要行動升級啊！我哋要罷工啊！我哋要係機場搞集會！我哋要輸出革命！<br />\n<br />\n過去兩個星期，勇武派付出太多啦，依家應該係和理非行動升級嘅時候！<br />\n<br />\n每人一小步，香港更美好！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:27:48.000Z","msg":"西九呢？都一樣可以輸出"},{"pid":"adf077f4160a7b1b5bb627e885cecd4ea1a54130","tid":1379961,"uid":14652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:27:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">打擊香港旅遊業<br />\n向外國人傳輸香港好危險<br />\n唔好來香港</span>"},{"pid":"a054cd8a9d4c0fa7d587dba4a729893bdfbc4b6a","tid":1379961,"uid":271333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:28:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e67d7335bda04f1dd3b726c848e2348b8402164c","tid":1379961,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:29:52.000Z","msg":"罷工"},{"pid":"35ad63d47b55105752e219d8ceacc3c4a5c4ff62","tid":1379961,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:30:07.000Z","msg":"罷工"},{"pid":"c1bca2e4420f67cda1010a4250208aeac65e0b96","tid":1379961,"uid":25951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:31:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2386e57a1c6bd98fc2701f0b99ab1771c734fa8","tid":1379961,"uid":156254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:32:10.000Z","msg":"一早講左流水式和平集會係最好<br />\n其他平民想參加都容易<br />\n每次要佔路及要衝, 又要承擔高風險比人拉仲衰吧"},{"pid":"32b7f2ea6150c2bda442d8f3f80a984fb8abcee1","tid":1379961,"uid":276481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:32:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ece9da5e7ecf2dcec61d7aebb2a010436a305aba","tid":1379961,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:33:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n2047到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"0e695c439ff1db2be746e2a7cf7838ea0445ec31","tid":1379961,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:35:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月29)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"94d1aa58304f344f3e0b712e7391fb07688da5f8","tid":1379961,"uid":235377,"like":0,"disl