nail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNVyktsn.png&h=32953479&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89d8333251d69162c9d5f7c33bd8d0911c101f7f","tid":1379961,"uid":278443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:42:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a18809684aff5728275503a1d58fc1abcbe47884","tid":1379961,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:42:46.000Z","msg":"罷工嗰班去機場lor"},{"pid":"c87d744299b540a384c24b74f210700a4e0b6757","tid":1379961,"uid":109701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:46:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77c8630c726bdc48a55f78156ae20aae0fda0191","tid":1379961,"uid":168541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:46:47.000Z","msg":"8.5一齊罷工"},{"pid":"fdc6490e4a3d243752861970a66a265c4b8607ac","tid":1379961,"uid":249187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c4996b658fbf7ef5d2fc4f90591d8bf4b0bec9","tid":1379961,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6bb83a559c05446dd105d48c45073234846f00","tid":1379961,"uid":180819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:50:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fefa3a130f5413b7f2e541e77fc23cc24cc2bda","tid":1379961,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c207533e1bbce5e0fe8616855c523671d3305da","tid":1379961,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:47:37.000Z","msg":"成日講警犬武力封頂，其實我哋都已經封左頂。<br />\n<br />\n雖然民意仲企係抗爭者一邊，但係我哋仲未逼到政府有任何根本性改變。<br />\n<br />\n因為到依家，我哋主要嘅抗爭手段未有根本性轉變。<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個禮拜，每一次行動，都係和理非遊行，到咁上下，勇武派同警犬開戰。<br />\n<br />\n每一次，柒婆只係需要出警犬同蓄龍已經頂得住，然後自己龜縮。<br />\n<br />\n每一次行動都拉3-40個勇武派，勇武派唔係無限人手架，拉一個就少一個架啦。<br />\n<br />\n如果依家嘅抗爭手段唔改變，當柒婆拉鳩晒啲勇武派之後，就正翻和理非上街，之後成個社運倒退翻去2014年之前。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋要做啲咩？我哋要行動升級啊！我哋要罷工啊！我哋要係機場搞集會！我哋要輸出革命！<br />\n<br />\n過去兩個星期，勇武派付出太多啦，依家應該係和理非行動升級嘅時候！<br />\n<br />\n每人一小步，香港更美好！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i7VU37d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi7VU37d.png&h=37389333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[抗議警黑合作] 全民港鐵戴頭盔 全民出街戴頭盔 日常<br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dpQDhS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dpQDhS</a>"},{"pid":"201e874db71aa439e3bd6a0fe5f6d296a101a456","tid":1379961,"uid":254860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:51:09.000Z","msg":"好想去機場參觀!"},{"pid":"fcb24556093e06ca499459cc54159516ac608a0b","tid":1379961,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:55:05.000Z","msg":"8月5號齊罷工"},{"pid":"a197fb9bef355fbff3a203fead6d24d26bfe4b70","tid":1379961,"uid":213781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:56:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c87c5257ec5dff141c86f76685b25808dc52344e","tid":1379961,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2769cd8940159bb7eb5b3fe228c8487b1f024be0","tid":1379961,"uid":287844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:01:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>需要機場做第一個集會嘅地方，<br />\n和應罷工，繼而各地鐵站，make noise </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"dea7257115afc56c4429c85511d8fab33bbada5c","tid":1379961,"uid":64624,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:02:16.000Z","msg":"罷工應該集體去機場！<br />\n班狗唔敢做d咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ecc84dcba79b26666bf09f22883